# checkbox-core-snap

This directory contains source code for all of the variants of checkbox-core-snap.
The variants being different snaps for different releases of Ubuntu.

`common_files` directory contains files that are shared between all series. By default they are not present in the corresponding series subdirectories.

# Snapping

Before you launch snapcraft, run `./prepare.sh` with an argument signifying which version of the snap you're planning to build. E.g.
```
./prepare.sh series22
```

